animeTitle: Nagano Toshi Gas x Kamiusagi Rope
animeDescription: A collaboration between Kamiusagi Rope and Nagano City Gas. The individual episodes were shown for 1 week on Nagano Broadcasting Systems official YouTube channel and website. Then later on the following Mezamashi Doyoubi (Saturday) broadcast.The goal was to inform people that Nagano City Gas' office has a wide variety of services such as a showroom showcasing remodeled gas kitchens, how to make sure you aren't losing money from bathroom heating, etc.
animeRelated: ['Other: Kamiusagi Rope: Warau Asa ni wa Fukuraitaru tte Maji ssuka!?']
